      <h3>
        <span class="comment-vote">
            <span id="c-723815635" class="vote-count">53</span>
              <a id="btn-723815635" href="" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="723815635">有用</a>

        </span>
        <span class="comment-info">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yuanmu/">袁牧</a>
            <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
          <a class="comment-time" href="/comment/723815635">2013-09-07 00:23:41</a>
          <span class="comment-location"></span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">“道路变得曲曲折折的”时，小说跌入蹒跚步行的的节奏中。我见过薰子，有过重叠群山、原始森林和深邃幽谷的旅行，连一声“心里扑通扑通的跳“都没让彼此感觉到，既是天涯沦落，必有一次别离，相识或为，万箭穿心。以后什么都没有留下，那到底曾经发生了什么。</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/1005521/?comment_id=723815635"></div>
    </div>
